name: The Agony Of Indecision Limited Edition Surreal Print Set by Teddy Pancake
description:
The Agony Of Indecision
These prints are beautiful full scale reproductions of one of my most popular paintings, The Agony of Indecision. The originals quickly sold but now you can hang these strange and compelling images on your own wall!

Giclée on Canson Photo Rag (310 gsm) Paper
Limited to 30 sets
Signed, Numbered & Titled by the artist
Printed with Ultrachrome archival pigment inks
Comes with a signed Certificate of Authenticity

Image Area 12 x 12”
Paper measures 14 x 14”

Shipping included to USA

More info at www.TeddyPancake.com
